    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then finely slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add your <strong>mayo </strong>to a small bowl with your <strong>shichimi togarashi</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a splash of <strong>cold water </strong>to loosen then stir it all together – this is your <strong>shichimi togarashi mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
