    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sushi rice</strong> with the <strong>miso chicken goujons</strong>,<strong> Asian-style peas</strong> and <strong>shichimi togarashi mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Garnish the rice with the <strong>remaining coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
